==Old Content== {{polluted category}} {{Wikipedia category|hidden=yes}} Articles in category contain all recorded . The statements may need to be updated, removed or edited for perspective. Articles containing older statements are more likely to be dated. This is '''not''' a backlog; not all articles included in this category will need updating at this point in time. See also [[:Category:Articles containing potentially dated statements]] which contains potentially dated statements ordered by originating date. Use {{tlx|As of}} to mark all individual statements that may become dated, this will automatically add them to the appropriate categories. Wherever possible, use {{tlx|Update after}} to mark exactly when statements will need updating in addition to using {{tlx|As of}}. {{Focusmessage}}
See also
* for details of dealing with statements that date quickly. * for guidelines on using precise language when dealing with information that may date quickly. * [[:Category:Wikipedia articles in need of updating]] and the accompanying {{tlx|Update after}} template. {{Navbox as of}} {{CatAutoTOC}}
